room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Tulsa in Tulsa
review: We had a great time. 3 adults and 3 kids ages 9-13. We selected Uptown Murder room since it was our first escape room experience. It was great that the younger kids still got to productively participate. We finished with 25 minutes left. I would definitely recommend this room if you have children with you.

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Tulsa in Tulsa
review: Absolutely awesome! Thank you for a wonderful 30th birthday!! We solved the Uptown Murder with some brains and a whole heck of a lot of luck! Lol!

room_title: Escape room "The Uptown Murder" by The Escape Tulsa in Tulsa
review: We had so much fun in the uptown murder room! Got out with 15 minutes to spare. Will definitely be back to do the other rooms!
